# GaudiAI Project Rules for Cursor

**IMPORTANT**: Always attach this `.cursorrules` file to every prompt when working on this project to ensure proper context and adherence to project standards.

## Project Overview
GaudiAI is an intelligent knowledge management and AI chat system built with modern web technologies. It features advanced security, internationalization, and scalable architecture with AI-powered conversations, knowledge management, and vector search capabilities.

## Architecture Overview
- **Backend**: FastAPI with async SQLAlchemy, PostgreSQL + pgvector, Celery + Redis
- **Frontend**: Vue 3 with Composition API, Vite, Vue Router, Vue I18n
- **Database**: PostgreSQL with pgvector extension for semantic search
- **Authentication**: JWT with token blacklisting, Google SSO integration
- **Background Tasks**: Celery with Redis broker
- **Containerization**: Docker & Docker Compose
- **Languages**: English (en) and Polish (pl) with dynamic switching

